{"tid":1324358,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"P牌建議","createTime":"2019-07-16T14:04:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T14:19:40.000Z","uid":249022,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6443963a522d4b9aad574872393f88a60d9274fe","tid":1324358,"uid":249022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:04:30.000Z","msg":"P牌唔可以必須有<br />\n當然呢一段時間一定要全部keep住<br />\n但係平靜左之後我覺得可以咁樣做<br />\n<br />\n登記日期距離而家&lt;100-150日 &amp; 上線時間&lt;60日 -&gt;可以撳掣除P一個星期(或者比特別P)(試用期)<br />\n1. 試用期內一定要七日有上線<br />\n少咗一日就要帶P多60日(從頭嚟過要上線多60日)<br />\n<br />\n2. 過咗試用期之後<br />\n嗰一個星期至少要上線3日<br />\n否則帶P多100日(從頭嚟過要上線多100日)<br />\n<br />\n3. 過咗2之後<br />\n一個月內要上線12日<br />\n每一個月-1日<br />\n到咗0之後就永久除P <br />\n如果失敗<br />\n會上返2<br />\n(由失敗嗰日開始計一個星期)<br />\n<br />\n如果1,2,3 夾埋失敗左4次<br />\n就永遠P牌<br />\n冇得救返<br />\n<br />\n知道好麻煩<br />\n但係都要比新會員一個機會<br />\n(同埋可以filter下五毛)<br />\nP牌必須有真係好慘<br />\n無啦啦俾人block<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n知道好亂<br />\n遲啲整圖"},{"pid":"048e3167400e3d267034d16d0db8df7618ff08ee","tid":1324358,"uid":260312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:06:14.000Z","msg":"話你on9怕你嬲"},{"pid":"ad043c05cf29dd88dd6493179a9aa126470cf4b9","tid":1324358,"uid":249022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"048e3167400e3d267034d16d0db8df7618ff08ee","tid":1324358,"uid":260312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:06:14.000Z","msg":"話你on9怕你嬲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:09:02.000Z","msg":"唔係可以點<br />\n七仔買卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b63c60b6ec374f838291c9bae0175fc99d6a9fe","tid":1324358,"uid":119283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:19:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 721 召集 請廣傳 </span></span>"}]}